9_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1958,"height":1100,"file_path":"/ghlu9afEq4XqLXFF2sLhIN2T5ac.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/yE4awb4H4Qr6WxE7nRoRhkl6cPc.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1958,"height":1100,"file_path":"/Pj6JkwcyfxvayXGINFJXQ786D4.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1958,"height":1100,"file_path":"/yoWZprrPpkBHHk79UG4MZsvezs1.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1958,"height":1100,"file_path":"/iGSzoIIbRDgvoAwVrsCCafevXwk.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1958,"height":1100,"file_path":"/7ljmqf0mD2g492oqyRZdiFEB9WN.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1958,"height":1100,"file_path":"/l0ukaVzP3IPvrPZZrjVV8uWXkiW.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1958,"height":1100,"file_path":"/pbQBnYUtKGlOWyX5KBrEebnbzG.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/zXuBWKfUquvBDHFngZzphb2qRUX.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/j0hBqgfWMoeFjCtGieIp0T9OqFx.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/qXWcXF1Va4EHf0gJLrdEJqlqYwa.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T10:18:23.143+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":93,"tagline":"Revenge has a new breed.","homepage":"https://muzzle.movie","overview":"LAPD officer Jake Rosser endeavors to lead a peaceful life with his family and retired K-9 officer, Socks. However, tranquility dissolves into chaos when a gang targets them in a brutal attack. Alongside his new K-9 partner Argos, Jake launches into a relentless pursuit of justice, determined to protect his loved ones."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"LAPD-officier Jake Rosser streeft ernaar een vredig leven te leiden met zijn gezin en gepensioneerde K-9-officier, Socks. Rust lost echter op in chaos wanneer een bende hen aanvalt. Samen met zijn nieuwe K-9-partner Argos begint Jake aan een meedogenloos streven naar gerechtigheid, vastbesloten om zijn dierbaren te beschermen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Клык 2: Город волков","runtime":93,"tagline":"Месть обретает новый облик.","homepage":"","overview":"Лос-Анджелес. Недолгая мирная жизнь бывшего полицейского-кинолога Джейка Россера рушится, когда банда жестоко нападает на его семью. С новым четвероногим напарником Аргосом он выходит на след сети наркоторговцев, бросает вызов коррумпированным чиновникам и борется со своими внутренними демонами."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"L'officier du LAPD Jake Rosser s'efforce de mener une vie paisible avec sa famille et l'officier retraité du K-9, Socks. Cependant, la tranquillité se transforme en chaos lorsqu'un gang les cible lors d'une attaque brutale. Aux côtés de son nouveau partenaire Argos, Jake se lance dans une quête incessante de justice, déterminé à protéger ses proches."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.capelight.de/muzzle-2","overview":"Der ehemalige K-9-Polizist Jake Rosser (Aaron Eckhart) versucht, die traumatischen Erlebnisse aus seiner Dienstzeit hinter sich zu lassen und ein ruhiges Leben mit seiner Familie zu führen. Als er jedoch ins Visier einer brutalen Gang unter der Führung des mysteriösen Totec gerät, schlägt der Frieden in Gewalt um. Zusammen mit seinem neuen K-9-Partner, dem Hund Argos, stellt sich Jake einem unerbittlichen Kampf um Gerechtigkeit. Dabei stößt er auf die korrupten Machenschaften eines skrupellosen Kartells und die Schatten seiner eigenen Vergangenheit – und riskiert alles, um das mörderische Netzwerk zu zerschlagen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ชีวิตอันสงบสุขของเจค อดีตเจ้าหน้าที่ K-9 ที่ถูกหลอกหลอน ต้องพังทลายลงเมื่อแก๊งค์หนึ่งโจมตีครอบครัวของเขาอย่างโหดเหี้ยม เขาร่วมมือกับอาร์กอส สหายใหม่จากหน่วย K-9 เพื่อเปิดโปงเครือข่ายค้ายา เผชิญหน้ากับเจ้าหน้าที่ทุจริต และต่อสู้กับปีศาจร้ายในใจขณะไล่ล่าอาชญากร"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"狼城驚魂","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"飽受創傷的前警犬訓導員傑克平靜的生活被一場幫派的殘忍襲擊徹底打破，他的家人遭到襲擊。他與新搭檔警犬阿爾戈斯一起，揭露了一個販毒集團，與腐敗官員對抗，並在追捕罪犯的過程中與內心的惡魔搏鬥。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"神探忠犬：狼之城","runtime":99,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"　　杰克·罗瑟曾是一名警犬训导员，因服役期间的创伤后应激障碍（PTSD）而饱受折磨，如今他努力与家人及退役警犬伙伴过着平静安宁的生活。然而，一场残酷的暴力袭击瞬间打破了这份宁静——一个残忍无情的帮派将他们锁定为目标。为了保护所爱之人，杰克与他的新警犬搭档“阿戈斯”深入罪恶滋生的黑暗世界，在那里，他不仅要面对腐败官员、揭开危险的毒品走私网络，更要直面自己内心的恶魔。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Farejando Vingança 2: Cidade dos Lobos","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Com o indicado ao Oscar Aaron Eckhart este thriller de ação mostra um ex-oficial K-9 que, após um ataque brutal à família, busca justiça com seu novo cão parceiro, enfrentando vingança, corrupção e guerra no crime."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Gdy gang atakuje rodzinę byłego policjanta K-9, Jake oraz Argos ruszają tropem narkotykowego kartelu, stając do walki z korupcją i własnymi demonami."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"머즐: 시티 오브 울브스","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"En Busca De Venganza 2: Ciudad De Lobos","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jake Rosser está atormentado por el trastorno de estrés postraumático de sus días como oficial K-9 y se esfuerza por llevar una vida pacífica con su familia y su compañero K-9 retirado, Socks. Pero la tranquilidad se disuelve rápidamente cuando una despiadada banda los persigue en un brutal ataque. Decidido a proteger a sus seres queridos, Jake y su nuevo compañero K-9 \"Argos\" se adentran en los violentos entresijos de la delincuencia, donde Jake se enfrenta a funcionarios corruptos, descubre una peligrosa red de tráfico de drogas y lucha contra sus propios demonios internos."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Viața liniștită a fostului ofițer Jake este distrusă când o bandă îi atacă brutal familia. Împreună cu noul său partener canin Argos, Jake descoperă o rețea de trafic de droguri, se confruntă cu oficiali corupți și se luptă cu propriii demoni în timp ce urmărește infractorii."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Муцуна: Град на вълците","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Джейк Росър — вече опитен бивш офицер от звеното за полицейски кучета — се опитва да живее спокоен живот със семейството си. Но спокойствието му е разклатено, когато жестока банда го нападна, насочвайки се към най-близките му. С нов четирикрак партньор Аргос, Джейк се впуска в опасно преследване, за да защити своите и да разкрие зловеща схема."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Nòng Súng: Hang Ổ của Sói","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jake Rosser sống yên ổn cùng gia đình và chú chó nghiệp vụ đã nghỉ hưu. Khi một băng nhóm tấn công họ, anh hợp tác với Argos, đối tác K-9 mới, để truy đuổi bọn tội phạm và bảo vệ gia đình."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"En busca de venganza 2: Ciudad de los lobos","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jake Rosser está atormentado por el trastorno de estrés postraumático de sus días como oficial K-9 y se esfuerza por llevar una vida pacífica con su familia y su compañero K-9 retirado, Socks. Pero la tranquilidad se disuelve rápidamente cuando una despiadada banda los persigue en un brutal ataque. Decidido a proteger a sus seres queridos, Jake y su nuevo compañero K-9 «Argos» se adentran en los violentos entresijos de la delincuencia, donde Jake se enfrenta a funcionarios corruptos, descubre una peligrosa red de tráfico de drogas y lucha contra sus propios demonios internos."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"חסר מעצורים 2: עיר הזאבים","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"חייו השקטים של ג׳ייק, שוטר לשעבר מיחידת כלבני קיי-9, נקרעים כשכנופיה תוקפת באכזריות את משפחתו. יחד עם שותפו החדש, הכלב ארגוס, הוא חושף רשת סמים, מתעמת עם אנשי ציבור מושחתים ונאבק בשדים הפנימיים שלו תוך כדי מרדף אחר הפושעים."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Petugas LAPD Jake Rosser berusaha menjalani kehidupan yang damai bersama keluarganya dan anjing pelacak pensiunan, Socks. Namun, ketenangan itu hancur berantakan ketika sebuah geng menyerang mereka dalam serangan brutal. Bersama dengan anjing pelacak barunya, Argos, Jake melancarkan pengejaran tanpa henti demi keadilan, bertekad melindungi orang-orang yang dicintainya."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Snukis: Vilkų miestas","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Buvęs K-9 būrio pareigūnas Džeikas Roseris, kamuojamas potrauminio streso sindromo, bando kurti ramų gyvenimą su šeima ir į pensiją išleistu tarnybiniu šunimi Soksas. Tačiau ramybė žlunga, kai negailestinga gauja surengia žiaurų išpuolį prieš jo artimuosius. Vedamas teisingumo troškimo, Džeikas kartu su naujuoju K-9 partneriu Argu pasineria į pavojingą nusikalstamą pasaulį. Kovodamas su korumpuotais pareigūnais ir pavojingu narkotikų prekybos tinklu, jis privalo nugalėti ir savo vidinius demonus, kad apsaugotų tai, kas jam brangiausia."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Jake Rosser (Aaron Eckhart), akit a K-9-es tisztként eltöltött időszaka óta poszttraumás stressz-szindróma kísért, igyekszik békés életet élni családjával és nyugdíjas K-9-es társával, Socksszal. A nyugalom azonban gyorsan szertefoszlik, amikor egy kegyetlen banda brutális támadással veszi célba őket. Jake és új K-9-es társa, Argos elszántan védi meg szeretteit, ezért belemerül a bűnözés erőszakos alvilágába, ahol Jake szembeszáll a korrupt tisztviselőkkel, leleplez egy veszélyes kábítószer-kereskedő hálózatot, és megküzd saját belső démonaival.  (Szarka Károly)"},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"LAPD-betjent Jake Rosser stræber efter at leve et fredeligt liv med sin familie og den pensionerede K-9-betjent, Socks. Men roen opløses i kaos, da en bande angriber dem brutalt. Sammen med sin nye K-9-partner Argos begiver Jake sig ud i en ubarmhjertig jagt på retfærdighed, fast besluttet på at beskytte sine kære."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"La vendetta ha una nuova generazione.","homepage":"","overview":"L'agente della LAPD Jake Rosser si impegna a condurre una vita tranquilla con la sua famiglia e l'ex ufficiale K-9, Socks. Tuttavia, la tranquillità si dissolve in caos quando una banda li prende di mira in un attacco brutale. Insieme al suo nuovo partner K-9 Argos, Jake si lancia in una incessante ricerca di giustizia, determinato a proteggere i suoi cari."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"694deffeec0d74776bb1c18e","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/694deffeec0d74776bb1c18e","author":"Chandler Danier","content":"There is enough in here to make you excited. The intro is cool. There are good action pieces. Good shots but it’s all glued together with like a confusing hour of crap. I have no idea why anything happened or why I had to watch bits without dogs doing cool stuff.\r\n\r\nIt’s fine though. Do you like dogs? Do you want to see dogs doing stuff? There are some cool dogs in this.","created_at":"2025-12-26T02:16:30.703Z","updated_at":"2025-12-26T02:16:30.714Z","author_details":{"name":"Chandler Danier","rating":6,"username":"chandlerdanier","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[],"similar_content":[{"id":942,"adult":false,"title":"Lethal Weapon 2","video":false,"overview":"Riggs and Murtaugh are on the trail of South African diplomats using their immunity to engage in criminal activities.","genre_ids":[28,12,35,80,53],"popularity":4.4713,"vote_count":3655,"poster_path":"/ZsUGxTnZ4TzTrHSAfUPJcliL1K.jpg","release_date":"1989-07-07","vote_average":7.026,"backdrop_path":"/zjRkl5PZvFujbRndrNbf4ZKbeNC.jpg","original_title":"Lethal Weapon 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":943,"adult":false,"title":"Lethal Weapon 3","video":false,"overview":"Riggs and Murtaugh pursue a former officer who uses his knowledge of police procedure and policies to steal and sell confiscated guns and ammunition to local street gangs.","genre_ids":[28,35,53,80],"popularity":3.5575,"vote_count":3148,"poster_path":"/smzJxEnusgqv3bvHIWwf4cuwPcr.jpg","release_date":"1992-05-15","vote_average":6.704,"backdrop_path":"/kmt9XmhmX36sJduuDVFlTgEWh9U.jpg","original_title":"Lethal Weapon 3","original_language":"en"},{"id":944,"adult":false,"title":"Lethal Weapon 4","video":false,"overview":"With personal crises and age weighing in on them, Riggs and Murtaugh must contend with deadly Chinese triads trying to free their former leaders from prison and onto American soil.","genre_ids":[28,12,35,80,53],"popularity":3.8392,"vote_count":2856,"poster_path":"/vl4n3uO602y8nDsqjE4RIMnSy8Q.jpg","release_date":"1998-07-10","vote_average":6.603,"backdrop_path":"/u4d4vymNPo1UuJ6ihtyy9OQgco2.jpg","original_title":"Lethal Weapon 4","original_language":"en"},{"id":10345,"adult":false,"title":"K-9","video":false,"overview":"The extravagant cop Michael Dooley needs some help to fight a drug dealer who has tried to kill him. A \"friend\" gives him a dog named Jerry Lee (Officer Lewis), who has been trained to smell drugs. With his help, Dooley sets out to put his enemy behind the bars, but Jerry Lee has a personality of his own and works only when he wants to. On the other hand, the dog is quite good at destroying Dooley's car, house and sex-life...","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"popularity":1.2065,"vote_count":1029,"poster_path":"/21mBNUe0X4WYywe6w5DyihltmAn.jpg","release_date":"1989-04-28","vote_average":6.164,"backdrop_path":"/vDBdstmX7z7g0yMQMWtWHJszJ4q.jpg","original_title":"K-9","original_language":"en"},{"id":562,"adult":false,"title":"Die Hard","video":false,"overview":"NYPD cop John McClane's plan to reconcile with his estranged wife is thrown for a serious loop when, minutes after he arrives at her office's Christmas Party, the entire building is overtaken by a group of terrorists. With little help from the LAPD, wisecracking McClane sets out to single-handedly rescue the hostages and bring the bad guys down.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":11.3985,"vote_count":12041,"poster_path":"/7Bjd8kfmDSOzpmhySpEhkUyK2oH.jpg","release_date":"1988-07-15","vote_average":7.806,"backdrop_path":"/bvk2AAH64lP2YZs02Q3jskfHT8j.jpg","original_title":"Die Hard","original_language":"en"},{"id":249021,"adult":false,"title":"Android Cop","video":false,"overview":"In the year 2045, a Los Angeles Police Department detective and his new android partner enter the Zone, a forbidden section of the city plagued with an unknown disease. There, they discover the source of the illness and attempt to stop it using the android's advanced technology and weaponry.","genre_ids":[28,878],"popularity":0.6339,"vote_count":73,"poster_path":"/pStgVcVSMNDykydPzMTuAiXAb50.jpg","release_date":"2014-02-04","vote_average":3.986,"backdrop_path":"/9DYCjWFD9iw5S7uunqqBj7lx77b.jpg","original_title":"Android Cop","original_language":"en"},{"id":602269,"adult":false,"title":"The Little Things","video":false,"overview":"Deputy Sheriff Joe \"Deke\" Deacon joins forces with Sgt. Jim Baxter to search for a serial killer who's terrorizing Los Angeles. As they track the culprit, Baxter is unaware that the investigation is dredging up echoes of Deke's past, uncovering disturbing secrets that could threaten more than his case.","genre_ids":[18,80,53],"popularity":7.0346,"vote_count":2739,"poster_path":"/tLO1aD1ghdtVMT32z2sRmzgYKYd.jpg","release_date":"2021-01-28","vote_average":6.337,"backdrop_path":"/vfuzELmhBjBTswXj2Vqxnu5ge4g.jpg","original_title":"The Little Things","original_language":"en"},{"id":13279,"adult":false,"title":"Lakeview Terrace","video":false,"overview":"A young interracial couple has just moved into their California dream home when they become the target of their next-door neighbor, who disapproves of their relationship. A tightly wound LAPD officer has appointed himself the watchdog of the neighborhood. His nightly foot patrols and overly watchful eyes bring comfort to some, but he becomes increasingly aggressive to the newlyweds. These persistent intrusions into their lives cause the couple to fight back.","genre_ids":[18,80,53],"popularity":2.023,"vote_count":1130,"poster_path":"/A1kqp2hALf8Gd03vDACnR0EtFWo.jpg","release_date":"2008-09-19","vote_average":5.976,"backdrop_path":"/6WfnLguRcpYQlJ6Wkx5CO7c8LpV.jpg","original_title":"Lakeview Terrace","original_language":"en"},{"id":11078,"adult":false,"title":"National Security","video":false,"overview":"Earl Montgomery, a bombastic police academy reject, and Hank Rafferty, a disgraced, mild-mannered cop, can't seem to escape each other. They met on opposite sides of the law during a routine traffic stop that escalated out of control; now as lowly security guards they're thrown together to bust a smuggling operation.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"popularity":2.9005,"vote_count":1041,"poster_path":"/8k6Qk2LiC3H1WWHxZXoXOVq89cS.jpg","release_date":"2003-01-17","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/bflP0bP1tx46zBNbq9Ba20sMWi7.jpg","original_title":"National Security","original_language":"en"},{"id":774370,"adult":false,"title":"Dog Man","video":false,"overview":"When a faithful police dog and his human police officer owner are injured together on the job, a harebrained but life-saving surgery fuses the two of them together and Dog Man is born. Dog Man is sworn to protect and serve—and fetch, sit and roll over. As Dog Man embraces his new identity and strives to impress his Chief, he must stop the pretty evil plots of feline supervillain Petey the Cat.","genre_ids":[10751,35,12,16,28],"popularity":4.7322,"vote_count":332,"poster_path":"/89wNiexZdvLQ41OQWIsQy4O6jAQ.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-24","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/w1SjvuBifhtFwe3BSssXXFyV6bk.jpg","original_title":"Dog Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":1538,"adult":false,"title":"Collateral","video":false,"overview":"Cab driver Max picks up a man who offers him $600 to drive him around. But the promise of easy money sours when Max realizes his fare is an assassin.","genre_ids":[18,80,53],"popularity":6.672,"vote_count":6119,"poster_path":"/nV5316WUsVij8sVXLCF1g7TFitg.jpg","release_date":"2004-08-04","vote_average":7.238,"backdrop_path":"/lEfZFNs5hr1Pgn4vpb7X31J927x.jpg","original_title":"Collateral","original_language":"en"},{"id":1637,"adult":false,"title":"Speed","video":false,"overview":"Tensions run high when a crazed bomber rigs a Los Angeles bus with a device that will kill everyone on board if the vehicle's speed dips below fifty miles per hour.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":7.5514,"vote_count":6698,"poster_path":"/82PkCE4R95KhHICUDF7G4Ly2z3l.jpg","release_date":"1994-06-09","vote_average":7.146,"backdrop_path":"/lywmuPU5Hr1Mnpb9UGeDbILmkTx.jpg","original_title":"Speed","original_language":"en"},{"id":7873,"adult":false,"title":"Harsh Times","video":false,"overview":"Jim Davis is an ex-Army Ranger who finds himself slipping back into his old life of petty crime after a job offer from the LAPD evaporates. His best friend is pressured by his girlfriend Sylvia to find a job, but Jim is more interested in hanging out and making cash from small heists, while trying to get a law enforcement job so he can marry his Mexican girlfriend.","genre_ids":[80,18,53,28],"popularity":1.6062,"vote_count":751,"poster_path":"/raBWBnGz2X6FQ3iUwPwYQE4FrkY.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-11","vote_average":6.435,"backdrop_path":"/lwK1HY1ml8bnTaQJzzcKfe2q93O.jpg","original_title":"Harsh Times","original_language":"en"},{"id":17494,"adult":false,"title":"Unlawful Entry","video":false,"overview":"Happily married Michael and Karen Carr call the police after Karen is held at knife point during a failed robbery attempt in their home. Before long, one of the responding officers, Officer Pete Davis, helps arrange the installation of a new security system, taking extra interest in the couple's case. As a result, the grateful Carrs invite him to stay for dinner and they strike up an unexpected friendship. However, as the lonely policeman develops an intense fixation on Karen, his take on friendship develops into a dangerous obsession soon becoming the Carrs' worst nightmare.","genre_ids":[53,9648],"popularity":1.1218,"vote_count":334,"poster_path":"/dvw1Pkt0tk8tvXy61cMwOaPgkyb.jpg","release_date":"1992-06-26","vote_average":6.223,"backdrop_path":"/gpzEfQEt5MQMIZaLbHpEj6rTiIW.jpg","original_title":"Unlawful Entry","original_language":"en"},{"id":31556,"adult":false,"title":"He Walked by Night","video":false,"overview":"Roy Martin aka Roy Morgan is a burglar and former war-time Radio & Electronics Engineer who listens in to radio police calls, allowing him to stay one step ahead of the cops.","genre_ids":[53,80],"popularity":0.628,"vote_count":100,"poster_path":"/wAhLdEjC9iIvF6Oly42Qs3LXKuL.jpg","release_date":"1949-02-06","vote_average":6.69,"backdrop_path":"/gKid6ohUtqZphz07N72VyP45cl8.jpg","original_title":"He Walked by Night","original_language":"en"},{"id":47354,"adult":false,"title":"K-9: P.I.","video":false,"overview":"Dooley and his K-9 partner Jerry Lee are ready to retire from the police force. But before he can retire with his pension he must work as a P.I. to find a set of high tech computer chips.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"popularity":2.054,"vote_count":205,"poster_path":"/2RdyzWbN3zTF1559GRnLbamy3V4.jpg","release_date":"2002-07-30","vote_average":5.917,"backdrop_path":"/1lwMWZFOtjiGqRwXvnkBgOMXH6S.jpg","original_title":"K-9: P.I.","original_language":"en"},{"id":1516295,"adult":false,"title":"Hard Justice","video":false,"overview":"Marine Grace Thompson joins the LAPD following the footsteps of her brother Michael. But when Michael is murdered, Grace must piece together the puzzle by following leads of corruption and cover-ups that run deeper than she ever imagined.","genre_ids":[28,53,80,18],"popularity":0.225,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/hulCVd0QwjCbsxxAUuzSbOoyZyA.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-01","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":"/3npibeCsXFqqHwJllxXOXDUhTFP.jpg","original_title":"Hard Justice","original_language":"en"},{"id":36278,"adult":false,"title":"Top Dog","video":false,"overview":"With his cop companion 